      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"different path\" sounds so out of reach though. Everything I know is this. Every connection I have, every bit of my identity... it's all tied to this research. If I walk away, there's nothing left. It's not just about a job, it's like I don't even exist outside of this failure. I'm just so drained. Like, I'm not even sad anymore, I'm just... done. I just want the noise to stop. I want to stop feeling like I'm constantly failing at being alive.",
